Test CRM Analytics Endpoints in Postman
Develop more quickly with the new CRM Analytics collection in Postman. Test endpoints using your own development environment, and view output instantly. Use these results to help you build your integrations with CRM Analytics.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions where CRM Analytics is enabled.
